      "date": "2023-09-26 07:55:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAndreas, should count be reseted by some timer or lfsck start? With a high uptime stack would not be repeated even after month.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "f5f002cbcc3c3c37f054e8bbd6cc1a6a701de6ba",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
